* Jika Aliff pilih NO, archive
* Jika Aliff pilih EDIT, revise row itu sahaja

SKIP RULE:
Skip mana-mana bisnes jika:

* Tiada public WhatsApp
* Tiada public phone
* Tiada clear public contact route
* Bisnes nampak inactive
* Big chain/franchise
* Data terlalu unclear
* Bukan appointment-based
* Sudah ada strong website + strong booking system

TARGET COUNT:
Cari 30 prospect jika mampu.
Jika tidak dapat 30 prospect dengan data usable, beri 15–20 prospect terbaik sahaja.
Kualiti data lebih penting daripada paksa cukup 30.

EXECUTION METHOD:
Guna 2-pass execution.

PASS 1 — FAST PROSPECT SCAN:
Cari 15–30 prospect yang:

* Niche relevant
* Area relevant
* Ada public WhatsApp / public phone / public contact route
* Appointment-based
* Ada weakness yang sesuai untuk Page Booking WhatsApp

PASS 2 — DEEP FILL TOP LEADS:
Untuk Top 10–15 prospect terbaik sahaja, deep-fill data untuk JSON import dengan semak:

* Google Business Profile
* Google Maps
* Official website
* Website Contact page
* Website About page
* Facebook Page About
* Facebook recent public posts
* Instagram public bio
* Public service/menu/promo posts
* Public Google review signals

